## ğŸ“Œ Project Overview  
The **Bidding Web Application** is a full-stack web project developed using **Python, Flask, SQL, HTML, CSS, and JavaScript**.  
It allows users to:  
- Register and log in  
- List items for bidding  
- Place bids on items in real-time  
- Securely manage user sessions and data  

This project was built as part of my **Python Web Developer Internship at ICT Academy**, completed within **two days** with my team.  

